strings:
<voice_0x010013A7><se_high>Red: Huh! That ain't somefin' I wanted ya to see.
And ya gone an' got the bounty to boot!

<voice_0x010013A8><se_high>Red: But 'ang on! Is that all it is?
That scraggy ol' bit o' paper!?
That's pathetic!

<voice_0x010013A9><se_high>Red: If I'd known it was as naff as that,
I'd never 'ave bothered!
<voice_0x010013AA><se_high>Red: I s'pose I'll just 'ave to make do with the 10,000 gold coins I picked up on the way.
<voice_0x010013AB><se_low>Yangus: Wotcher! You lot awright, are ya?

<voice_0x010013AC><se_high>Red: Blimey! Shout a bit louder, will ya?
Ya noisy great lummox...
<voice_0x010013AD><se_low>Yangus: Red! I, I didn't know you were 'ere, too.

<voice_0x010013AE><se_high>Yangus: Hmph, a fine greetin' that is, eh?
Pleased to see you an' all.

<voice_0x010013AF><se_low>Yangus: Nah, I didn't mean...
I d-didn't mean it...
<voice_0x010013B0><se_low>Yangus: Well anyway, I see ya got wot ya came for.
<voice_0x010013B1><se_low>Yangus: ...Meanin' there ain't no point 'angin' 'round 'ere any more! Let's 'op it, eh?
<voice_0x010013B2><se_low>Yangus: Here, d'you score all that dosh in this cave? Blimey, yer a crafty devil, intcha?
<voice_0x010013B3><se_low>Yangus: We got wot we came for, any'ow.
<voice_0x010013B4><se_low>Yangus: ...Meanin' there ain't no point 'angin' 'round 'ere any more! Let's 'op it, eh?

<voice_0x010013B5><se_low>Yangus: Well, we got wot we we came for, any'ow.
Time to make tracks.
<voice_0x010013B6><se_high>Red: Wait up!
<voice_0x010013B7><se_high>Red: I'll come wiv ya.
<voice_0x010013B8><se_low>Yangus: You wot?

<voice_0x010013B9><se_high>Red: You know me, I've got a nose for treasure.
And I reckon you lot stink of it.
<voice_0x010013BA><se_low>Yangus: Leave it out, Red. We ain't messin' around 'ere, awright? This is serious business.
<voice_0x010013BB><se_high>Red: I don't remember askin' for permission. Me mind's made up, so you can like it or lump it.

<voice_0x010013BC><se_low>Yangus: Oh, suit yerself.
I was only tryin' to be consid'rate.
<voice_0x010013BD><se_low>King Trode: Well, I think it's a splendid idea!
<voice_0x010013BE><se_low>Yangus: COR BLIMEY!
<voice_0x010013BF><se_low>King Trode: The girl wishes to join our illustrious band, does she not? Well, the more the merrier, I say! Safety in numbers, and so on!
<voice_0x010013C0><se_low>Yangus: Oh, not you an' all.
<voice_0x010013C1><se_low>Yangus: Fine. Just don't say I didn't warn ya.

<voice_0x010013C2><se_high>Red: That's settled, then.
I'll tag along wiv you lot for a bit.
Red joins the party!
<voice_0x010013C3><se_high>Red: Awright, I'll see you lot on the boat, then.
